{"type": "article", "id": 4130, "title": "Menu 珠宝首饰盒", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-05T08:25:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052330555zoqtRMWdslLKxQE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自哥本哈根的建筑与家具设计师 Theresa Arns 日前为丹麦设计品牌 Menu 带来一款珠宝首饰盒的设计。Theresa Arns 出生于德国，实用成为她设计时的首要考虑因素，但她又不想因此缺失了温暖而诗意的部分，于是选择用简单的几何形状来勾勒这款珠宝盒，盒子内部的分区确保了用户将珠宝、化妆品等按需归纳，贴心的内部镜子装置即是为了方便用户化妆与戴取珠宝时随手使用。提供白橡木、黑槐木以及深色白蜡木三种材质可选，定价 599 丹麦克朗（约合人民币 610 元），<a href=\"http://menu.as/shop/accessories/storage/jewellery-box-white-oak\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233053JZkRn94jSPrITUOa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233053fS5PBZa2JY7boltG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233054mFAg7Gvsdra5QEM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233054mEFWeUAdLOr924Ho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}